'''Mario Pirani Coen''' (3 August 1925 <U+2013> 18 April 2015) was an [[Italy|Italian]] journalist, economist, and writer.

== Biography ==
Born in Rome, he became a member of the [[:it:Association of Journalists|Association of Journalists]] of [[Lazio]] in January 1958. Politically closed to the [[Italian Communist Party]], he left it after the Soviet invasion of Hungary in 1956.<ref>{{cite web|title=Mario Pirani confessa di aver sbagliato tutto Ma ne va ancora fiero|url=http://www.ilgiornale.it/news/mario-pirani-confessa-aver-sbagliato-tutto-ne-va-ancora.html|accessdate=21 March 2015|language=Italian}}</ref> He later became an offficer of ''[[Eni]]''.

After the experiences with ''[[:it:Pattuglia (rivista)|Patrol]]'', ''[[Il Giorno (newspaper)|Il Giorno]]'' and [[:it:Il Globo (1945-1983)|Il Globo]], he participated, together with [[Eugenio Scalfari]], to the foundation of ''[[la Repubblica]]'', a newspaper that became one of the first in Italy. He became the Deputy Director, with [[:it:Gianni Rocca|Gianni Rocca]] and [[:it:Giampaolo Pansa|Giampaolo Pansa]]. 
He was also editor of [[L'Europeo]] from 1979 to 1980, succeeding [[:it:Giovanni Valentini (giornalista)|Giovanni Valentini]]. In 1995 he won the [[Premiolino]].

He died in Rome on 18 April 2015, aged 89.<ref>{{cite news|title=Addio a Mario Pirani, giornalista e scrittore|url=http://www.lastampa.it/2015/04/18/cultura/addio-a-mario-pirani-giornalista-e-scrittore-tRMf3BzY2782xA5XUPe0oL/pagina.html|accessdate=19 April 2015|work=La Stampa|date=18 April 2015|language=Italian}}</ref>

== Works ==
* The charm of Nazism. The case Jenninger: a controversy about the history, Il Mulino, 1989, pp.&nbsp;157, ISBN 88-15-02337-2.<ref>{{cite book|last1=Pirani|first1=Mario|title=Il fascino del nazismo : il caso Jenninger : una polemica sulla storia|date=1989|publisher=Societ<U+00E0> editrice il Mulino|location=Bologna|isbn=88-15-02337-2}}</ref>
* The future of the economy seen by leading Italian economists, Arnoldo Mondadori Editore, 1993, pp.&nbsp;229, ISBN 88-04-36582-X.<ref>{{cite book|last1=Pirani|first1=Mario|title=Il futuro dell'economia : visto dai maggiori esperti mondiali|date=1993|publisher=A. Mondadori|location=Milano|isbn=88-04-36582-X|edition=1. ed.}}</ref>
* You broke the third world war? Democracies between pacifism and defense, Arnoldo Mondadori Editore, 2004, pp.&nbsp;302, ISBN 88-04-54624-7.<ref>{{cite book|last1=Pirani|first1=Mario|title=<U+00C8> scoppiata la terza guerra mondiale? : le democrazie tra pacifismo e difesa|date=2005|publisher=A. Mondadori|location=Milano|isbn=88-04-54624-7|edition=Nuova ed.}}</ref>
* It could be worse. Half a century of reasonable illusions, Arnoldo Mondadori Editore, 2010, pp.&nbsp;430, ISBN 88-04-59360-1.<ref>{{cite book|last1=Pirani|first1=Mario|title=Poteva andare peggio : mezzo secolo di ragionevoli illusioni|date=2010|publisher=Mondadori|location=Milano|isbn=88-04-59360-1|edition=1. ed.}}</ref>

